{"id":176,"date":"2025-08-29T02:20:33","date_gmt":"2025-08-28T20:50:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp\/?page_id=176"},"modified":"2025-08-31T02:49:38","modified_gmt":"2025-08-30T21:19:38","slug":"clubs-sponsored-by-us","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/clubs-sponsored-by-us\/","title":{"rendered":"Clubs Sponsored by us"},"content":{"rendered":"        <section class=\"ispl-hero-wrap\" style=\"background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/about-bls-club.jpg');background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/about-bls-club.jpg'); \">\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-overlay\" style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-inner\" style=\"position:relative; max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:6rem 1.25rem;\">\r\n                                    <h2 style=\"font-size:3rem; line-height:1.1; margin:0 0 1rem;\">Nurturing Leadership, Expanding Service \u2013 Sponsored Clubs of Lions Club of Balasore<\/h2>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"font-size:1.125rem; max-width:800px;\">\u201cEvery great movement grows stronger when it inspires others to lead. The Lions Club of Balasore takes pride in sponsoring and guiding new clubs, planting seeds of service that flourish into vibrant communities of change. These sponsored clubs are not just extensions of our mission\u2014they are living legacies of compassion, leadership, and unity. Each new Lion carries forward the torch of service, lighting up more lives and strengthening the bond of humanity. Together, we form a chain of hope that stretches beyond boundaries, proving that when one club grows, an entire community thrives. Sponsorship is more than support\u2014it is mentorship, empowerment, and the promise that the spirit of service will endure for generations to come.\u201d<\/p>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"margin-top:2rem;\">\r\n                        <a href=\"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/our-leaders\/\" class=\"ispl-hero-btn\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:.9rem 1.5rem; background:#ffcc00; color:#111; text-decoration:none; border-radius:.35rem; font-weight:600;\">\r\n                            Our Leaders                        <\/a>\r\n                    <\/p>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n        <\/section>\r\n        \n        <div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n            <table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered align-middle text-center\">\r\n                <thead class=\"table-light\">\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <th scope=\"col\">#<\/th>\r\n                        <th scope=\"col\">Name \/ Title<\/th>\r\n                        <th scope=\"col\">Year<\/th>\r\n                    <\/tr>\r\n                <\/thead>\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>1<\/td>\r\n                        <td>Lions Club of Bhadrak<\/td>\r\n                        <td>1981<\/td>\r\n                    <\/tr>\r\n                                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>2<\/td>\r\n                        <td>Leo Club of Balasore<\/td>\r\n                        <td>1982<\/td>\r\n                    <\/tr>\r\n                                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>3<\/td>\r\n                        <td>Lionees Club of Balasore<\/td>\r\n                        <td>1985<\/td>\r\n                    <\/tr>\r\n                                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>4<\/td>\r\n                        <td>Lions Club of Balasore Sand City<\/td>\r\n                        <td>1998<\/td>\r\n                    <\/tr>\r\n                 